---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Meet Dr. Nathan Beyerl - San Diego chiropractor focused on education, autonomy, and sustainable improvement for adults 55+.">
  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section__eyebrow">About The Bridge</span>
      <h1>Meet Dr. Nathan Beyerl</h1>
      <p>Your partner in moving better and living fuller.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Intro -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-image">
          <img src="/images/IMG_0954.JPG" alt="Dr. Nathan Beyerl - San Diego Chiropractor" />
        </div>
        <div class="about-content">
          <h2>Healthcare That Empowers</h2>
          <p class="lead">I own and operate The Bridge Chiropractic, a movement-focused wellness clinic here in San Diego. My approach is simple: healthcare should give you control over your own health.</p>
          <p>Too many people experience rushed appointments, standardized treatment plans, and providers who don't take time to listen. I founded The Bridge to offer something different—calm, trust-based care that prioritizes your long-term function and independence.</p>
          <p>When you visit my clinic, you'll notice the difference immediately. I take time to listen to your concerns, explain what's happening in your body, and collaborate with you on a plan that fits YOUR goals—not a one-size-fits-all protocol.</p>

          <div class="about-stats">
            <div class="stat">
              <span class="stat__number">15+</span>
              <span class="stat__label">Years Experience</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <span class="stat__number">500+</span>
              <span class="stat__label">Patients Helped</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <span class="stat__number">5.0</span>
              <span class="stat__label">Google Rating</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Philosophy -->
  <section class="section section--gray">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section__header">
        <span class="section__eyebrow">My Approach</span>
        <h2 class="section__title">Philosophy of Care</h2>
        <p class="section__subtitle">Three pillars that guide every patient interaction.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid--3">
        <div class="philosophy-card">
          <div class="philosophy-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"></path><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Education Over Dependency</h3>
          <p>I want you to understand your body. When you know WHY something hurts and HOW to prevent it, you're empowered to take control of your own health.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="philosophy-card">
          <div class="philosophy-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Sustainable Improvement</h3>
          <p>Quick fixes rarely last. I focus on long-term solutions that help you stay active and pain-free for years to come, not just until your next appointment.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="philosophy-card">
          <div class="philosophy-card__icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"></circle></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Personalized Care</h3>
          <p>What one patient needs might be completely different from another. I create individualized care plans designed around YOUR body and YOUR goals.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What to Expect -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="expect-grid">
        <div class="expect-content">
          <span class="section__eyebrow">Your First Visit</span>
          <h2>What to Expect</h2>
          <p>Your first visit is all about understanding you. Here's what happens when you walk through our doors.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="expect-steps">
          <div class="expect-step">
            <div class="expect-step__number">1</div>
            <div class="expect-step__content">
              <h3>We Listen</h3>
              <p>Your appointment starts with a thorough conversation. I want to understand your health history, current concerns, and what you hope to achieve.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="expect-step">
            <div class="expect-step__number">2</div>
            <div class="expect-step__content">
              <h3>We Assess</h3>
              <p>A comprehensive evaluation helps us understand what's happening in your body. I'll explain my findings in clear, simple terms.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="expect-step">
            <div class="expect-step__number">3</div>
            <div class="expect-step__content">
              <h3>We Plan Together</h3>
              <p>We'll create a personalized care plan together—one that fits your lifestyle, respects your preferences, and works toward your goals.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Credentials -->
  <section class="section section--dark">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="credentials-grid">
        <div class="credentials-content">
          <span class="section__eyebrow">Qualifications</span>
          <h2>Credentials & Training</h2>
          <p>Committed to continuous learning and the highest standards of care.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="credentials-list">
          <div class="credential-item">
            <div class="credential-item__icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 10v6M2 10l10-5 10 5-10 5z"/><path d="M6 12v5c3 3 9 3 12 0v-5"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span>Doctor of Chiropractic (D.C.)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="credential-item">
            <div class="credential-item__icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><path d="M9 15l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span>Licensed in California</span>
          </div>
          <div class="credential-item">
            <div class="credential-item__icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 16v-4M12 8h.01"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span>Specialized training in neuro/brain rehabilitation</span>
          </div>
          <div class="credential-item">
            <div class="credential-item__icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span>Certified in movement and mobility assessment</span>
          </div>
          <div class="credential-item">
            <div class="credential-item__icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span>Continuing education in geriatric care</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2>Ready to Experience the Difference?</h2>
      <p>Schedule your first visit and see what calm, personalized care feels like.</p>
      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--white btn--lg">Book Your Visit</a>
        <a href="tel:8582777500" class="btn btn--outline-white btn--lg">Call (858) 277-7500</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Page Hero */
  .page-hero {
    background: var(--color-off-white);
    padding: 140px 0 80px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .page-hero p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-dark);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* About Grid */
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-4xl);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-image img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .about-content .lead {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-2xl);
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
    padding-top: var(--space-xl);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-gray-light);
  }

  .stat {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat__number {
    display: block;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat__label {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-dark);
    margin-top: var(--space-xs);
  }

  /* Philosophy Cards */
  .philosophy-card {
    background: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-light);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .philosophy-card__icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--color-primary-light);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-lg);
  }

  .philosophy-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .philosophy-card p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-gray-dark);
  }

  /* Expect Grid */
  .expect-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 350px 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-4xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .expect-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .expect-content p {
    color: var(--color-gray-dark);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .expect-steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .expect-step {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    background: var(--color-off-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }

  .expect-step__number {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .expect-step__content h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .expect-step__content p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-gray-dark);
  }

  /* Credentials Grid */
  .credentials-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-4xl);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .credentials-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .credentials-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .credentials-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .credential-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .credential-item__icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(113, 196, 233, 0.2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .credential-item span {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-section {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0;
  }

  .cta-section h2,
  .cta-section p {
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .cta-section p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .cta-section p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .cta-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .about-grid,
    .credentials-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-2xl);
    }

    .about-image {
      order: -1;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .expect-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-xl);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-hero {
      padding: 120px 0 60px;
    }

    .about-stats {
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .stat__number {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .page-hero {
      padding: 100px 0 40px;
    }

    .about-stats {
      gap: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .philosophy-card {
      padding: var(--space-lg);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .expect-step {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .expect-step__number {
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .cta-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .cta-actions .btn {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
